{"title":"学习英雄","authors":["辛而"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":11,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习英雄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辛而"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炊事班长李德新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习文化下决心；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咱三十六岁不识字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睁着两眼象瞎子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三月整军时间长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓紧机会去学习。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戒了香烟省下钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笔墨纸张先买全；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"津贴虽少慢慢集，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三月买了枝金星笔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习方法弄清楚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里长征第一步。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炊事班，十弟兄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"名和姓，先认清；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手榴弹，卡宾枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"名称表，钉上墙；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘴里念，心里记，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一撇一划要仔细。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大麦羹，稻米饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面煮，一面念；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炉、锅、刀、板，葱、韭、大蒜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七天学习，完全会念。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧火时灰上写，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厕所里地上写，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面写一面念，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚上睡觉温一遍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七天认五十，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半月一百几；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个多月能写墙报稿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全连数他呱呱叫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不自满，不骄傲；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最低目标还没到："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“半年要看解放报。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九，十一，十六于上海"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}